rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0010
rows.name: Looks like another batch of Samaarian records.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0020
rows.name: "The six fetters rob this one of all thought.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0030
rows.name:
"Even a deathless child of Samaar
cannot slip free of these bonds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0040
rows.name:
"This one's mind will eternally diminish,
until his essence mayhap expires within the rift."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0060
rows.name:
So the Samaarians made this prison for Void,
to trap him here until the end of time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0070
rows.name: But it didn't quite play out that way...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0100
rows.name:
But there's one thing we've learned:
these devices are sure to work on Void.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33200130_MSG0120
rows.name: Armed with this, we may yet gain the upper hand.[ST:wait ]
